```json
{
  "application": "Slurm",
  "details": {
    "software": [
      "Bowtie2",
      "SAMtools",
      "BEDTools"
    ],
    "resources": {
      "memory": "96gb",
      "time": "05:59:00",
      "cpu": 8
    },
    "input": [
      "SAMPLE_LIST (file containing sample IDs)",
      "../VIR_DB/virus_contigs/w_neg_der95_index/w_neg_der95 (Bowtie2 index)",
      "../SAMPLES/${SAMPLE_ID}/clean_reads/${SAMPLE_ID}_dedup_paired_1.fastq.gz (read file 1)",
      "../SAMPLES/${SAMPLE_ID}/clean_reads/${SAMPLE_ID}_dedup_paired_2.fastq.gz (read file 2)",
      "../SAMPLES/${SAMPLE_ID}/clean_reads/${SAMPLE_ID}_dedup_unmatched.fastq.gz (unmatched reads)",
      "../VIR_DB/virus_contigs/w_neg_der95_index/w_neg_der95.bed (BED file)"
    ],
    "output": [
      "${TMPDIR}/${SAMPLE_ID}/ALIGN/${SAMPLE_ID}_w_neg_der95.sam (SAM alignment file)",
      "${TMPDIR}/${SAMPLE_ID}/ALIGN/${SAMPLE_ID}_w_neg_der95.bam (BAM alignment file)",
      "${TMPDIR}/${SAMPLE_ID}/ALIGN/${SAMPLE_ID}_w_neg_der95.sorted.bam (sorted BAM file)",
      "${TMPDIR}/${SAMPLE_ID}/ALIGN/${SAMPLE_ID}_w_neg_der95.sorted.bam.bai (BAM index file)",
      "../VIR_DB/mapping/VLP_to_w_neg_der95/coverage/${SAMPLE_ID}.coverage.txt (coverage file)",
      "../VIR_DB/mapping/VLP_to_w_neg_der95/alignment_log/${SAMPLE_ID}.bowtie2.log (alignment log file)"
    ]
  }
}
```
